                  <p><img style="max-width: 100%" src="{{ asset('uploads/custom/images/1934.png') }}" alt="1934.png"></p>
                  <p>Il faut faire attention aux instructions suivantes:</p>
                  <p><img style="max-width: 100%" src="{{ asset('uploads/custom/images/1935.png') }}" alt="1935.png" width="620" height="129" /></p>
